#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.32"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.32:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.32:0.2"
msgid "4. Sīsapāvanavagga"
msgstr "4. In a Rosewood Forest"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 32. Khadirapattasutta → khadirasuttaṃ (bj) | khadiro (pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.32:0.3"
msgid "32. Khadirapattasutta"
msgstr "32. Acacia Leaves"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.32:1.1"
msgid "“Yo, bhikkhave, evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "“Mendicants, suppose someone were to say:"

msgctxt "sn56.32:1.2"
msgid ""
"‘ahaṃ dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ yathābhūtaṃ anabhisamecca, dukkhasamudayaṃ "
"ariyasaccaṃ yathābhūtaṃ anabhisamecca, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ "
"yathābhūtaṃ anabhisamecca, dukkhanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ ariyasaccaṃ "
"yathābhūtaṃ anabhisamecca sammā dukkhassantaṃ karissāmī’ti—"
msgstr ""
"‘Without truly comprehending the noble truths of suffering, its origin, its "
"cessation, and the path, I will completely make an end of suffering.’"

msgctxt "sn56.32:1.3"
msgid "netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr "That is not possible."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.439"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.32:2.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, yo evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "It’s as if someone were to say:"

# See BB for identification of sarala. He reads talapakka for talapatta, commenting that talapatta doesn’t make good sense. I think it’s the other way around. The fruit is a small thing, easily carried in a little basket. The whole point is that it would absurdly impossible to carry a huge palm frond in a basket made of such small leaves.
#. VAR: saralapattānaṃ → salalapattānaṃ (bj) | palāsapattānaṃ (s1, s2, km, pts1) | saralasapattānaṃ (s3)
msgctxt "sn56.32:2.2"
msgid ""
"‘ahaṃ khadirapattānaṃ vā saralapattānaṃ vā āmalakapattānaṃ vā puṭaṃ karitvā "
"udakaṃ vā tālapattaṃ vā āharissāmī’ti—"
msgstr ""
"‘I’ll make a basket out of acacia leaves or pine needles or myrobalan "
"leaves, and use it to carry water or a palm frond.’"

msgctxt "sn56.32:2.3"
msgid "netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati;"
msgstr "That is not possible."

msgctxt "sn56.32:2.4"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, yo evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "In the same way, suppose someone were to say:"

msgctxt "sn56.32:2.5"
msgid ""
"‘ahaṃ dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ yathābhūtaṃ anabhisamecca … pe … "
"dukkhanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ ariyasaccaṃ yathābhūtaṃ anabhisamecca sammā "
"dukkhassantaṃ karissāmī’ti—"
msgstr ""
"‘Without truly comprehending the noble truths of suffering, its origin, its "
"cessation, and the path, I will completely make an end of suffering.’"

msgctxt "sn56.32:2.6"
msgid "netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr "That is not possible."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.32:3.1"
msgid "Yo ca kho, bhikkhave, evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "But suppose someone were to say:"

msgctxt "sn56.32:3.2"
msgid ""
"‘ahaṃ dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ yathābhūtaṃ abhisamecca, dukkhasamudayaṃ "
"ariyasaccaṃ yathābhūtaṃ abhisamecca, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ yathābhūtaṃ "
"abhisamecca, dukkhanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ ariyasaccaṃ yathābhūtaṃ "
"abhisamecca sammā dukkhassantaṃ karissāmī’ti—"
msgstr ""
"‘After truly comprehending the noble truths of suffering, its origin, its "
"cessation, and the path, I will completely make an end of suffering.’"

msgctxt "sn56.32:3.3"
msgid "ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
msgstr "That is possible."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.32:4.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, yo evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "It’s as if someone were to say:"

msgctxt "sn56.32:4.2"
msgid ""
"‘ahaṃ padumapattānaṃ vā palāsapattānaṃ vā māluvapattānaṃ vā puṭaṃ karitvā "
"udakaṃ vā tālapattaṃ vā āharissāmī’ti—"
msgstr ""
"‘I’ll make a basket out of lotus leaves or flame-of-the-forest leaves or "
"camel’s foot creeper leaves, and use it to carry water or a palm frond.’"

msgctxt "sn56.32:4.3"
msgid "ṭhānametaṃ vijjati;"
msgstr "That is possible."

msgctxt "sn56.32:4.4"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, yo evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "In the same way, suppose someone were to say:"

msgctxt "sn56.32:4.5"
msgid ""
"‘ahaṃ dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ yathābhūtaṃ abhisamecca … pe … "
"dukkhanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ ariyasaccaṃ yathābhūtaṃ abhisamecca sammā "
"dukkhassantaṃ karissāmī’ti—"
msgstr ""
"‘After truly comprehending the noble truths of suffering, its origin, its "
"cessation, and the path, I will completely make an end of suffering.’"

msgctxt "sn56.32:4.6"
msgid "ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
msgstr "That is possible."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.32:5.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.32:5.2"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
